{"tid":1924372,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［13/3 TVB日任］陳凱琳代言Lux洗頭水 繼續做任賀TVB股價跌至個位數","createTime":"2020-03-13T15:53:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T13:00:59.000Z","uid":48083,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e69c59d4273a034104e1e147bd9970e7498777a4","tid":1924372,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T15:53:55.000Z","msg":"［轉載，唔好幾千人俾正皮多謝完又唔幫手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />］<br />\n<br />\n是日喜訊<br />\n<strong>CCTVB股價創新低</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q7GCBai.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq7GCBai.jpg&h=4d76d5e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想TVB收皮記得叫埋身邊朋友CLS我地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n700萬thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【偽人狙擊@Mar 13】<br />\n💎LUX x 外星琳💎<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/LuxHongKong/posts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FLuxHongKong%2Fposts%2F&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7jxVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=6a936ae0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/LuxHongKong/posts/</a><br />\n😠1.派嬲 🗣2.洗版 🙅🏻&zwj;♀️3.罷買 👍🏻4.互Like留言<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/ghlchan.official/posts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fghlchan.official%2Fposts%2F&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7jxVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=10e242e2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/ghlchan.official/posts/</a><br />\n👆🏽😭勸佢早日離開TVB👆🏽<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XMSeDp1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXMSeDp1.jpg&h=ffbe15cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n洗頭水大把選擇，絕對唔會用人血水黎洗頭！😡<br />\n<br />\n#LUX #陳凱琳<br />\n<br />\n1.派嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 2.請願<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 3.推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 4.永久抵制 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. 互like留言，推上FB留言熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">※留言template</span></strong><br />\n<blockquote>抵制TVB運動已開始半年，貴公司仍然用無綫電視藝人作代言實屬不智，本人深表遺憾，並呼籲貴公司停止與無綫藝人合作，否則將永久抵制貴公司，敬請注意。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n歡迎用呢幾幅圖留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WKS01k8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWKS01k8.jpg&h=219c86da&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oh33Y7O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOh33Y7O.jpg&h=3bb0e7dd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QXpe5NO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQXpe5NO.png&h=ac508817&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;我是分隔線&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n［<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">進階任務</span></strong>］<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/22HRFDJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F22HRFDJ.jpg&h=c6193287&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n⚠️升級行動⚠️<br />\n由於「KUKA」效法block人始祖TVB隱藏留言，我哋係時候升級喇❗️<br />\n1️⃣ <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">電郵</span></strong>投訴📧<br />\n cs@kukahome.com.hk<br />\n電郵Template：<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/KUKA_HOME\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FKUKA_HOME&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7jxVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=07375374\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/KUKA_HOME</a><br />\n<br />\n2️⃣ <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">舉報</span></strong>專頁及帖文 (▶️海關/消委會成日留意嗰個原因)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/KUKAhongkong/posts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FKUKAhongkong%2Fposts%2F&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7jxVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=d7442e14\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/KUKAhongkong/posts/</a><br />\n<br />\n3️⃣ 派嬲🤬、留言貼醜聞 (💢記得<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">關鍵字要隔空格&quot;C C T V B&quot;</span></strong>)<br />\n<br />\n📌【TVB春袋: 廣告商抵制名單】📌<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻 電子ver <a href=\"http://bit.ly/tvbadver\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Ftvbadver&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7jxVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=4a9ba07e\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/tvbadver</a> 👈🏻<br />\n👉🏻 文宣ver <a href=\"http://bit.ly/tvbposter\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Ftvbposter&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7jxVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=f164a4a3\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/tvbposter</a> 👈🏻<br />\n<br />\n⚠抵制TVB戰線 @sayno2tvb<br />\nTG群: @Sayno2cctvb<br />\nFB: <a href=\"http://www.fb.com/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fb.com%2Fsayno2tvb&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7jxVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=aabc52d7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.fb.com/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsayno2tvb&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7jxVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=a9a172c6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.instagram.com/sayno2tvb</a>"},{"pid":"dcb557a71d1ba18e9b0d07c07ea53a3a9ad00ccc","tid":1924372,"uid":40521,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T16:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/OGJOBMw.png\" />"},{"pid":"7338617f09cba5c73f94768174607632e40c6c04","tid":1924372,"uid":56023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T18:15:56.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"7b3f79d9268e786a7b2be0d3f6ba2e3bff3ac859","tid":1924372,"uid":40521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit